    <span class="text-white text-3xl" style="font-family:serif; position:absolute; right:22%; top:20%"> <span class="italic">Dialexicon</span> Vol. 3, 2023</span>    <!-- <span class="text-white text-2xl absolute left-20 top-44" style="font-family:serif"> Bringing philosophy to youth. </span>
