        <span> I. Has Science Disproven Free Will?</span>
        <span class="ml-1 italic text-blue-200"> Yi An Chan</span>
      </a>
      <a href="./essays/sasha" class="flex flex-row gap-1 hover:italic hover:text-blue-200 hover:border hover:border-white p-2 rounded-xl">
