        <span class="ml-1 italic text-blue-200"> Sasha Johnson</span>
      </a>
      <a href="./essays/bernadett" class="flex flex-row gap-1 hover:italic hover:text-blue-200 hover:border hover:border-white p-2 rounded-xl">
